room_title: Escape room "Operation North Pole" by iPanic Escape Room in Lakeland
room_description:
Worried about getting nothing but coal this year for Christmas!?
Well this is your chance to fix that! Break into Santa's Magical workshop with your friends and find clues to hunt down The Naughty List! You will have 60 minutes to steal The Naughty List before Santa and his Elves return!
